label.value: Rapid Access to Intervention Development

value.value: RAID is a new program designed to facilitate translation to the clinic of novel, scientifically meritorious therapeutic interventions originating in the academic community. It will do this by making available to the academic research community, on a competitive basis, NCI resources for the pre-clinical development of drugs and biologics.
